      </div>
      <div class="stat-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff3cd,#ffe699);">
        <div class="num" style="color:#b38600;">5 hrs</div>
        <p>The shortest December day in Helsinki provides fewer than <strong>5.7 hours of daylight</strong> — often overcast and heavily filtered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8f4ec,#c0e8cc);">
        <div class="num" style="color:#2a7a4b;">10 000</div>
